<materialsCitation id="6ECE3CCDB73028420A92F9A03C09F970" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3804722315" pageId="21" pageNumber="411">Colombia, restricted by P. Hershkovitz in 1949 to El Tambor, Rio Labrija, 25 km north-west of Bucaramanga, Santander, Colombia.</materialsCitation>
